{{作品名稱|name=''The Jazz Singer''|hk=爵士巨星|tw=爵士歌手|cn=爵士歌手}}是一部1980年的美國劇情電影，也是1927年經典電影《[[爵士乐歌星|爵士乐歌星]]》的重拍版。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-jazz-singer-1980 |title = Reviews: The Jazz Singer |author = Roger Ebert |date = 1980-12-22 |publisher = RogerEbert.com |language = en |accessdate = 2016-06-30 |archive-date = 2016-07-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160701072503/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-jazz-singer-1980 |dead-url = no }}</ref>主演是[[尼爾·戴門|尼爾·戴門]]、[[羅蘭士·奧利花|羅蘭士·奧利花]]和{{link-en|Lucie Arnaz|Lucie Arnaz}}，由{{link-en|理查德·弗萊徹|Richard Fleischer}}及{{link-en|Sidney J. Furie|Sidney J. Furie}}聯合執導。

